snippet.title: SovereignDev
snippet.description:
I'm the solo Developer of a game called "Sovereign"
Sovereign is an RPG inspired by other great games such as "Skyrim", "The Witcher Series", and a little "Animal Crossing"
If you enjoy my content try to catch me during my streams over on Twitch
   https://www.twitch.tv/sovereigndev
